column12: The root form of the word. For e.g., "ask" is the root word of "asked"
The words that have the common base word. For e.g.,  "asked" and "asking" are related words as they have common base word "ask"
This implies base word that were not in the "Word List".  For e.g., "abaci" base word is "abacus" but it is not in the "Word List", so it is marked green
